description:
Goto marches forward relentlessly to discover the identity of his tormentor, the man who had Goto locked up in a private prison for ten long years without ever telling him why. But Goto's nemesis wants Goto to find him, and meet they do, as Goto's enemy reveals his identity and gives Goto clues that suggest this decade-long ordeal stems from a long-forgotten schoolyard grudge. But there's more to this cruel game, and Goto's friends may end up in the morgue if he doesn't agree to continue the game-in sudden death!

  • Chapter 50: Grace Mizukoshi
  • Chapter 51: Class Reunion
  • Chapter 52: Sudden Death

name: Vol. 6

description:
Imprisoned without explanation for a decade, Goto is a free man at last, but what price freedom? Now, his mysterious jailer, a former schoolmate with a lifelong grudge, has Goto embroiled in a malicious game to discover the reasons behind the schoolyard vendetta and why his tormentor would go to such extreme lengths to exact his retribution. It's bad enough when Goto discovers that his memories have been impeded by hypnotic conditioning, but when he learns that his lover, too, is a victim of hypnotic manipulation, Goto begins to suspect that she may be an unwitting pawn in his enemy's venomous endgame!

  • Chapter 60: Shooting Star Epiphany
  • Chapter 61: Buildup
  • Chapter 62: Test Song

  • Chapter 64: Song Aphasia
  • Chapter 65: Left Bank of the Sumida River
  • Chapter 66: Escape from Kyojima
  • Chapter 67: Contact
  • Chapter 68: The Enemy at Hand
  • Chapter 69: Deeper
name: Vol. 7

description:
Imprisoned without explanation for a decade by a wealthy former schoolmate, Goto now comes to the endgame against his tormentor. If Goto cannot uncover the secret behind the schoolyard grudge, he'll earn his death and the death of the girl he loves-just as his adversary will accept death if Goto can unlock his memories and the meaning behind them. But there's more to the game locked away in memories, and even the end of the game may not mean the end to the war!

  • Chapter 71: Limit
  • Chapter 72: Seven Days

  • Chapter 74: Until Tuesday
  • Chapter 75: Northward
  • Chapter 76: Time's Up
  • Chapter 77: Song Source
  • Chapter 78: Loneliness
  • Final Chapter: Town of Flowers
  • Epilogue

name: Vol. 1

description:
Nightcrawler! Shadowcat! Captain Britain! Meggan! And the return of Rachel Summers, the Phoenix! As our heroes team with Captain America, Iron Man and Black Panther to save Wakanda, Phoenix battles Galactus in space! And back in England, the government is trying to take control of the nation's super heroes, but it's not going well - just ask the Warpies!

Then, it's a trip to a Sentinel-ruled future - and the shocking origin of Widget! Alan Davis returns to Excalibur for some of the team's greatest adventures yet!

Collecting EXCALIBUR (1988) #59-67.
name: Volume 3

description: For years, Thor lived on Earth as protector, champion and Avenger - endearing himself to the entire world. Having lived a mortal's life, Earth's well-being was of paramount importance to the Asgardian God of Thunder. His ascension to the throne interfered with that mission. Asgard's interests forced Thor to ignore Earth. So wielding a power only the greatest of gods might possess, Asgard's liege transported his realm to the skies above Manhattan, the better to guide and protect the whole of humanity. Now, see how the Thunder God's presence on Earth affects the lives of people both ordinary and extraordinary - and not for the better. Collecting THOR (1998) #59-67 and material from MARVEL DOUBLE-SHOT #1.
name: Thor: Spiral

description:
When Wolverine faces a problem of the villainous kind, there's a good chance he'll use his Adamantium claws to whip up a lethal solution to it. What happens, though, when he faces an opponent who becomes a much bigger problem if he's killed?

Enter: Contagion, a bold new addition to Wolverine's rogues' gallery. But first, Logan must contend with Contagion's defenders, the aptly named crew known as the Unkillables.

Collecting WOLVERINE: THE BEST THERE IS #1-6.
name: HC/TPB

volume.name: Wolverine: The Best There Is: Contagion

description: X-Factor is in upheaval as one member leaves, another arrives, and Rictor and Rahne finally have it out over the identity of her baby's father! Plus: a high-school student's suicide of triggers X-Factor's most personal case. And when a man is killed by what seems to be vampires, can the team separate fact from fiction? Then, Mayor J. Jonah Jameson thrusts NYC's premiere detective agency into the midst of a murder investigation, but the trail seems to lead them straight back to...Jonah himself?! Collecting X-FACTOR (1986) #213-219.
name: Volume 12
Una storia di Natale
Conto alla rovescia
La vita segreta di Sergej Orloff

description: New York is hit by a series of catastrophic events modeled on the " ten plagues of Egypt " and orchestrated by a scientist in search of revenge against the city . Who is this unknown " evil genius " ? And why has he unleashed his fury on the " Big Apple " ? Flanked by a fascinating biologist , Martin Mystere is following the case
name: Le dieci piaghe

description: A mystery  75,000 years old takes  Martin on Roanoke Island , in whose ground lies the most dangerous place for the whole human race : the prison of the Red King . The mysterious entity ha s been guarded for millennia by the Elohim , but is about to awaken. Or maybe it is already awake .
name: Il Re Rosso
Paperinik e la minaccia di Electroduck

description: A mysterious killer with ESP powers  hunts an even more mysterious character , while Martin tries to help a Russian special agent to stop him. And Java  guides them, following the telepathic instructions of Maria , in a race against time .
name: L'angelo del male

description: An Italian family has guarded for centuries some ancient manuscripts related to the Palazzo della Ragione in Padua . That same building is the key that closes the pit of demons in Khemtar , the mythical city of Hermes Trismegistus . The Master of the cult of Celaphas Elects wants to come to the well to open it , while Martin and Java , along with italian archaeologist Alessia Zambonin , with the help of  Erickson and the Men in Black, try to stop him.
name: La città dei maghi
Super Dingo et la bonne étoile

description: Martin Mystere is grappling with yet another mysterious and dangerous book in the footsteps Lawrence of Arabia , followed by Maxwell and a strange monster made ​​of minced meat, controlled by an exiled monk.
name: Il numero della bestia
Oncle Picsou retrouve la reine du Klondyke

description: The visit of the brother of Java takes once more Martin in the port city of Ethereal Shadows , while a sinister character is preparing for the return of extraterrestrials to comply with the agreement that he had formed with the Empress of Mu.
name: Il segreto delle Ombre Diafane
Oncle Picsou et le trésor des Kiabu-Boâra
Picsou et Tarcent la terreur des grands fauves
Oncle Picsou super danseur de Saingui-Bondi

description: An “artistic” mystery awaits Martin Mystère, in the form of a version of the “Mona Lisa” by Leonardo da Vinci, slightly different from the original, but executed with equal mastery of the medium, and above all comparably old. The work exerts enormous power of attraction over an unscrupulous collector, who has no compunction about stealing it. In order to discover the story which hides behind this “impossible” painting, Martin goes to Milan in search of a clarifying document…
name: Il sorriso venuto dal passato

description: Martin Mystère, Diana and Java are in the North of Italy to investigate the origin of a mysterious “Mona Lisa”, a painting apparently the twin of Leonardo’s “Mona Lisa”, but with a few strange differences compared to the original. Their search will take them to a thirteenth-century stronghold, which conceals an incredible secret …
name: Operazione Monna Lisa

description: In the city of Ardiss , Brendon discovers he has an identical twin by the name of Blaine . Accused of a murder he did not commit, the knight venture should find him to demonstrate his innocence.
name: Il riflesso del male

description: Brendon asks the help of Zeder, a sorcerer who is said to have the power of time travelling,  to try to stop the murdering of his mother .
name: Ritorno al passato

description: In New Dream there are the appearances of some fairies, beautiful winged creatures that leave a trail of blood on their way .
name: Le fate azzurre uccidono

description: Shrouded by a dark fog bank that changes the day into a murky night, the ship of the immortal Captain, Akhar Nun, endlessly roams the seven seas. But the vampire Master holds a secret, hidden in a mysterious island that cannot be found on nautical charts: that’s where Harlan, Kurjak and Tesla are waiting for him, on that cursed rock where Akhar Nun lost his one true love...
name: La nave fantasma

description: From Haiti to Chicago, from Nogales to Vegas! And it's just the first part of a breath-taking adventure: in Chicago, vampire policeman Jim Fajella is trying to catch the director of NEA, Benson, with Harlan and Kurjak's help. Meanwhile in Nevada, Lenny Meyer, now commissioner of LVPD, is involved in a fraudulent scheme and accused of having killed an FBI agent. Harlan have some suspicions about Bugsy Siegel, but the undead gangster – now completely blind – has seemingly retired. And what's the part in this story of the former serial killer/avenger Jeff Carter, now a zombie on the isle of Haiti?...
name: Trappola a Las Vegas

description: The undead abandoned by the deceased Master of the Night, Ixtlán, found a new boss, and Bugsy Siegel is instructed to organize them and face his enemies — Harlan, Kurjak and Jim Fajella. They will surely come to Vegas, to try and save their friend Lenny Meyer, wanted for a fake murder charge. Meanwhile, the avenger/serial-killer Jeff Carter arrives to the United States... All the knots of the story will be untied, in a bloody night in Vegas...
name: La vendetta di Bugsy

description: Blue Road Jones is a Dakota Sioux: the path that brought him to Chicago lies under a deadly sign. When a young girl, Jenny Clearwater, his betrothed, finds out that Jones is charged with a string of ruthless murders, leaves her reservation to go to the city. Blue's totem is the wolf... So, is he the “werewolf” that's drenching the nights of Chicago in blood? Meanwhile, Harlan Draka is on the serial killer's tracks, too...
name: Lo spirito del lupo

description: During the Yugoslavian Civil War, Kurjak was forced to execute one of his comrade-in-arms, Captain Gorislav, after the soldier went crazy. Among the ranks of the Montenegrin Mafia, though, there's a man called "The Prince" who looks just like Gorislav: to uncover his secret, Harlan and co. try to pass for criminals as well...
name: Il cuore di Gorislav

description:
Overview:
 

The controversial 242-page follow-up to Understanding Comics advocates 12 different revolutions in the way comics are created, distributed and perceived with special emphasis on the potential of Online Comics.

Part One examines comics as an art form and as literature, creator's rights, the changing business of comics, public perception, and gender and ethnic diversity.

Part Two explores comics and new technology, including digital production, digital distribution, and the design challenges of comics in a digital environment.
name: Reinventing Comics

description:
Overview:

If you’ve ever felt there must be something more to making comics than just copying drawing styles then this is the book for you.

Topics include:

  • Choosing the right moments—what to include, what to leave out.

  • Framing actions and guiding attention.

  • Choosing words and images that communicate together.

  • Creating varied and compelling characters with inner lives and unforgettable appearances.

  • Understanding body language and facial expressions.

  • Creating rich, believable worlds for your readers to explore.

  • Picking the tools that are right for you.

  • Navigating the world of styles and genres.

Supplement

name: Making Comics
